<section class="founder" data-screen-label="Founder note">
  <div class="founder__inner">
    <div class="founder__photo reveal"><img src="/assets/photos/team-rich-scherf.png" alt="Rich Scherf, founder of Cardo" loading="lazy" /></div>
    <div class="founder__body reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our humble beginning</p>
      <blockquote class="founder__quote">"It started as one experiment — a single home listed on Airbnb while I was still working a full-time job. I had no idea it would become my life's work."</blockquote>
      <p>Then COVID hit. Two hundred–plus cancellations came through in a matter of weeks, and everything I'd built was suddenly on the line. We didn't fold. We rebuilt — moved to a straight commission model so owners only win when we win, tightened every part of our operation, and came out the other side stronger than we went in. That "no-fail" attitude is baked into how we run every home today.</p>
      <p>Everything since has been in service of one desire: to build a brand owners trust, with homes they can be proud of.</p>
      <div class="founder__sig"><b>Rich Scherf</b><span>Founder &amp; CEO, Cardo Vacation Rentals</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
